>Go to https://discordapp.com/developers/applications/ >Create a new application >Put 'CLIENT ID' in textbox
>Go to 'Rich Presence' >Add image to 'Rich Presence Assets' (If you want) >Image asset is the name of the image, >This is the image displayed with your status!
>Image text >Main Status
>Details >Details about status
>Party Size >Display a fake 'Party Size'
>If you have problems >Try adding RPC in discord [Game Activity]
